string-array.name: array_fixed_common_phrase
string-array.item: "Ka kira wayar ofis dina, na gode."
"Ka kira wayar salulata anjima, na gode."
"Na fita waje, je gida, zan kira."
"Ina kan hanya, za mu hadu nan take."
"Cunkoson ababen hawa, yi hakuri, sai anjima."
"Ina cikin taro, zan ba da amsa anjima."
